name: Pack of 6 - Digital
description:
Buy the 6 issues for 50% off full price!
This is a pack of 5 digital Tiny Feet publications incliding:

#1 Soft and Pastel Colors
#2 Dreamy Fairytales
#3 Baby It's Cold Outside
#4 The Circus Parade
#5 Summer Loving
#6 Welcome to Candyland

All 5 issues will be sent to you as digital publications for download which you can then use across all your personal devices (iPad, iPod Touch, iPhone, android, etc.)

This way you can add each issue of Tiny Feet to, for example, your iBooks library and view it when ever you feel like it.

Within 2 to 48hours after payment is cleared you will receive an email with the files for download.

We will use your paypal email to send the files, unless you contact asking to send to another one.
